43:12.718 --> 43:13.927
Work is prayer, Robyn.

43:14.011 --> 43:16.221
Then I prayed the whole Bible.

43:16.889 --> 43:17.890
Good lass.

43:20.392 --> 43:21.810
This is still new for you,

43:21.894 --> 43:24.104
but it's a righteous life
for a young lady.

43:24.188 --> 43:25.814
Well, it's no life for me.

43:25.898 --> 43:28.358
I can get the Wolfwalkers to leave.
You just need to listen to me--

43:28.442 --> 43:30.485
Robyn Goodfellowe, enough of your stories.

43:30.569 --> 43:31.570
I can go look for her--

43:31.653 --> 43:34.072
You must do as you're told.
No more fairy tales.

43:34.156 --> 43:35.157
-But the--
-No buts.

43:35.240 --> 43:37.451
-The Wolfwalkers--
-Wolfwalkers are not real.

43:50.172 --> 43:52.549
They are real. Right, Merlyn?

44:28.168 --> 44:30.462
Merlyn, can you smell that?

44:31.463 --> 44:33.090
Merlyn, what's happened to you?

44:34.049 --> 44:35.551
I can see your scent.

44:38.136 --> 44:42.641
What? Oh, no. Oh, no. Oh, no, no.

44:45.894 --> 44:50.315
What? What do I do? How did this happen?
Oh, no, no, no.

44:54.194 --> 44:56.321
-Wolf! Wolf! Robyn, wake up!
-Father, help!

45:00.617 --> 45:02.911
No, no, no, Father. It's me! Father!

45:18.760 --> 45:19.761
What was that?

45:20.637 --> 45:21.972
Did you see that?

45:41.783 --> 45:42.993
Mebh!

46:02.721 --> 46:03.847
