47:03.407 --> 47:05.367
Of course. Everybody can.

47:05.951 --> 47:07.786
Well, close your eyes.

47:10.038 --> 47:12.624
You don't need your eyes to see.

47:13.208 --> 47:17.004
And you can hear
every little thing that moves.

47:19.339 --> 47:22.092
And your paws can hear through the earth.

47:22.176 --> 47:24.219
