50:29.571 --> 50:32.741
No! Nobody can catch my mammy.

50:33.909 --> 50:36.453
Sorry. How long has she been gone?

50:36.537 --> 50:37.538
Since...

50:38.956 --> 50:43.085
She's all right. She'll be back soon.
She promised.

50:44.127 --> 50:47.881
Well, don't worry. Wherever she is,
we'll find her. I can help you.

50:47.965 --> 50:49.716
Yeah! There's two of us now.

50:49.800 --> 50:51.552
I'll sneak out
and meet you back here tomorrow.

50:51.635 --> 50:54.388
I'll be waiting for you, again!

50:54.471 --> 50:57.850
Mebh, we'll find her.
Then you can all leave and be safe.

50:58.392 --> 51:00.060
You promise?

51:00.143 --> 51:01.144
I promise.

52:30.734 --> 52:32.736
Hey, wolf! Get it!

52:33.779 --> 52:35.531
Wolf, there! Shoot!

52:39.284 --> 52:40.452
Wolf! Wolf in the town!

52:40.536 --> 52:42.037
-Wolf!
-Wolf in the town!

52:42.120 --> 52:43.455
Oh, my God!

52:48.335 --> 52:50.295
Lord Protector won't be happy!

52:55.300 --> 52:57.010
-Open it now!
-The wolf!

52:58.303 --> 52:59.346
Wolf.

53:01.223 --> 53:02.391
Get it, now!

53:02.474 --> 53:04.393
-Yes, sir!
-Load your muskets! Surround the beast!

53:05.269 --> 53:06.770
-Kill the wolf!
-Kill the wolf!

53:06.854 --> 53:08.438
Kill it! Kill the beast!

53:09.356 --> 53:10.315
Fire!

53:12.943 --> 53:14.444
Get rid of that wolf!

53:15.654 --> 53:17.865
Goodfellowe, what is this?

53:20.075 --> 53:25.247
Enough! I will deal with this wolf myself.
Now, back to your beds.

53:32.671 --> 53:34.590
-Do you see it?
-Where'd it go?

53:34.673 --> 53:36.383
Keep looking. It's here somewhere.

53:52.316 --> 53:53.817
That scent.

53:53.901 --> 53:55.903
-I knew it!
-Wolf in the castle!

53:55.986 --> 53:57.154
Do you see it?

53:57.237 --> 53:59.239
Search every corner.

53:59.615 --> 54:01.325
Don't let it get away!

54:03.160 --> 54:04.369
Girl.

54:06.914 --> 54:07.915
Girl.

54:08.999 --> 54:10.459
Girl, here. Quick.

54:24.932 --> 54:26.266
Hello?

54:27.226 --> 54:30.729
Only a Wolfwalker can make another.
When did it happen to you? Where?

54:30.812 --> 54:33.232
Is the wolf that bit you near?
Is she all right?

54:33.315 --> 54:35.442
Is she alive? Where is Mebh?

54:37.778 --> 54:40.864
You're Mebh's mother.
Wait till I tell her I found you.

54:40.948 --> 54:43.534
She'll be so happy.
She's waiting for you in the forest.

54:43.617 --> 54:45.869
You mean she's still here? In the woods?

54:45.953 --> 54:48.330
No, no, no! She must go!

54:48.413 --> 54:50.707
But we have to rescue you.
How do I get you out?

54:51.500 --> 54:53.377
Wolf! Wolf in the castle!

54:53.460 --> 54:55.254
You'll be killed like this.

54:55.337 --> 54:57.339
Listen, girl, get back
to your human body right away.

54:57.422 --> 54:58.632
If I can just get the--

54:58.715 --> 55:00.801
She should never have bitten you.

55:00.884 --> 55:04.096
Get Mebh and leave.
It's not safe for our kind here.

55:04.179 --> 55:06.974
-But Mebh won't leave without you.
-She must not come for me.

55:07.057 --> 55:10.227
She must not wait for me.
She must run. And you too, girl.

55:10.310 --> 55:11.311
Now!

55:34.751 --> 55:37.254
Lord, what must I do?

55:37.337 --> 55:40.382
I left to quell rebellion
and returned to more.

55:40.966 --> 55:44.136
This wild land must be civilized.

55:44.219 --> 55:46.388
That is Your will.

55:52.769 --> 55:53.770
So, wolf,

55:53.854 --> 55:56.940
tomorrow I will show them
I have tamed you,

55:57.024 --> 55:59.651
just as I will tame this land.

56:00.444 --> 56:05.115
They will have nothing to fear
if they trust in the Lord's will.

56:06.241 --> 56:07.451
-What the--
-Go!

56:09.411 --> 56:11.997
Tell Mebh to lead the pack to safety.

56:12.080 --> 56:13.540
Go! Now!

56:49.868 --> 56:51.119
How do I do this?

56:51.745 --> 56:53.580
Come on, come on.

56:58.043 --> 56:59.211
Come on.

57:02.631 --> 57:04.007
Robyn, are you awake?

57:04.091 --> 57:06.510
-What, Father?
-There was a wolf here in our chambers.

57:06.593 --> 57:08.929
Got in while you were sleeping.
It could have taken you.

57:09.012 --> 57:10.013
Father, I was--

57:10.097 --> 57:12.599
This world is such a dangerous
place for you, lass.

57:13.350 --> 57:15.811
-I promised I would keep you safe.
-But that--

57:18.939 --> 57:21.441
-Come with us.
-Lord Protector wants a word with you.

57:21.525 --> 57:23.277
Back, I say!

57:23.360 --> 57:26.321
Ironsides! What are you doing about it?

57:28.866 --> 57:32.327
Goodfellowe.
A wolf here, threatening the town.

57:32.411 --> 57:35.706
It got inside the castle
in my very chambers.

57:35.789 --> 57:37.624
-This is intolerable.
-Sir, I--

57:37.708 --> 57:40.294
Enough! You have failed.
You are no hunter.

57:40.377 --> 57:43.630
From now on, you will serve in my ranks
as a foot soldier.

57:46.592 --> 57:50.637
-Townspeople! Order, please! Order! Order!
-Silence.

57:51.138 --> 57:53.140
Tomorrow, I will show you all.

57:53.223 --> 57:57.811
I will tame this land.
I will find that den.

57:57.895 --> 58:00.731
Every last wolf will be destroyed.

58:00.814 --> 58:02.441
No! Stop!

58:02.524 --> 58:03.609
There is another way!

58:03.692 --> 58:05.944
Release her, the Wolfwalker.

58:07.112 --> 58:08.197
Wha--

58:08.280 --> 58:10.782
Please! You must listen!

58:11.575 --> 58:12.743
Take her to the stocks.

58:12.826 --> 58:14.203
-No! Sir, please!
-Stop that!

58:14.286 --> 58:16.538
She's just a child.
And I know these woods.

58:16.622 --> 58:18.790
-I can still help you on your mission.
-Silence!

58:21.418 --> 58:24.213
It's safe now! Go to your beds!

58:24.296 --> 58:27.716
Tomorrow, I will make good on my word.

58:27.799 --> 58:29.092
Guards! Guards!

58:29.176 --> 58:32.471
-Move it! Move along, now!
-Get out of here!

58:32.554 --> 58:36.225
Goodfellowe,
I will give you both one more chance.

58:36.308 --> 58:38.727
Follow your orders
or you'll be off to war.

58:38.810 --> 58:39.811
Yes, my lord.

58:39.895 --> 58:41.438
And, girl, come here.

58:42.940 --> 58:45.943
Never speak of such pagan nonsense
in this town.

58:46.026 --> 58:50.572
Follow the rules or you will never see
your father again. Do you understand?

58:51.114 --> 58:52.533
Yes, my lord.

58:53.367 --> 58:55.452
Double the guard. Bar the gate.

58:55.536 --> 58:58.413
No more wolves inside these walls.

58:58.497 --> 59:00.207
Yes, sir. On the double!

59:06.255 --> 59:10.467
Listen to me. We must follow our orders
if we are to stay together.

59:10.884 --> 59:13.554
You must do as you're told, my girl.

1:00:27.002 --> 1:00:31.089
Made a new friend, Mammy.
A townie, but a nice one.

1:00:31.632 --> 1:00:32.883
Her name is Robyn.

1:00:32.966 --> 1:00:35.761
She's taller than me, but I'm stronger.

1:00:35.844 --> 1:00:38.889
And she brushed my hair
and gave me this flower.

1:00:38.972 --> 1:00:41.350
And she's from a place called England.

1:00:41.433 --> 1:00:43.685
And we're gonna meet
by the oak tree tomorrow.

1:00:44.186 --> 1:00:46.021
And she promised to help.

1:00:46.104 --> 1:00:49.233
And-- Where are you?

1:00:50.317 --> 1:00:54.613
You promised you'd come back,
but it's been so long now.

1:00:55.155 --> 1:00:58.075
Are you lost?
Has something happened to you?

1:00:59.243 --> 1:01:02.955
Robyn will help me find you, Mammy.
She promised.

1:01:03.622 --> 1:01:05.165
There's two of us now.

1:01:07.876 --> 1:01:12.089
Seoithín seothó

1:01:12.172 --> 1:01:16.093
Seoithín seothó

1:01:24.059 --> 1:01:25.853
Robyn, time for work.

1:01:40.117 --> 1:01:42.452
Merlyn, I can't get out to Mebh.

1:01:42.536 --> 1:01:44.913
Find her. Tell her to leave.

1:01:44.997 --> 1:01:47.416
Lead her away. She must go.

1:01:48.917 --> 1:01:50.669
At least you can be free.

1:02:03.015 --> 1:02:04.558
It's for your own good, lass.

1:02:51.605 --> 1:02:53.649
Birdie! About time.

1:02:53.732 --> 1:02:55.567
Robyn, what you took you so long?

1:02:58.403 --> 1:03:01.198
Robyn! Where are you?

1:03:03.575 --> 1:03:05.953
What do you mean
she can't come out of the town?

1:03:09.206 --> 1:03:13.085
I'm not leaving. She promised.
Help me find her, Merlyn.

1:03:46.994 --> 1:03:48.495
Where were you?

1:03:49.746 --> 1:03:51.248
Mebh, what are you doing here?

1:03:51.331 --> 1:03:53.792
I waited for ages!

1:03:53.876 --> 1:03:55.335
You're supposed to be gone from here.

1:03:55.419 --> 1:03:56.753
I sent Merlyn to tell you.

1:03:56.837 --> 1:03:59.256
What's that, girl? Who are you talking to?

1:03:59.339 --> 1:04:00.924
Nobody.

1:04:01.675 --> 1:04:04.678
I've forgotten about them knots.
They're supposed to be done.

1:04:04.761 --> 1:04:07.181
You must go, Mebh.
Lead the pack away to safety.

1:04:07.264 --> 1:04:10.559
I told you. I'm not leaving
without my mammy.

1:04:14.313 --> 1:04:16.398
Mebh, you have to listen to me.

1:04:16.481 --> 1:04:19.026
You must leave the forest.
Take the wolves and go.

1:04:19.610 --> 1:04:21.737
But... you said you'd help me.

1:04:21.820 --> 1:04:25.282
-I am helping you, the only way I can.
-You promised.

1:04:25.365 --> 1:04:29.036
The Lord Protector will burn the woods.
He will kill all the wolves by sunset.

1:04:29.119 --> 1:04:31.705
You have to get them out.
Do you understand?

1:04:34.208 --> 1:04:35.292
Now go.

1:04:37.336 --> 1:04:40.923
You said you would help me. You promised.

1:04:42.508 --> 1:04:46.720
Go, Mebh. Take Merlyn with you. Goodbye.

1:05:16.041 --> 1:05:17.668
I hear he's got a wolf.

1:05:17.751 --> 1:05:21.463
I hear it's a giant beast to behold.
Much bigger than a wolf.

1:05:21.547 --> 1:05:24.550
-Mammy?
-Won't that be a sight.

1:05:25.676 --> 1:05:28.679
Do you suppose he's going to kill it?

1:05:28.762 --> 1:05:31.515
Oh, yes. 'Tis a monster.

1:05:31.598 --> 1:05:33.684
-Mammy!
-Crazy child!

1:05:33.767 --> 1:05:35.143
-Careful, girl!
-Watch out!

1:05:35.227 --> 1:05:37.437
You'll hurt someone like that.

1:05:39.773 --> 1:05:43.235
Come on now, ladies.
Everyone's to go to the courtyard.

1:05:46.488 --> 1:05:50.659
The Lord Protector wants
everyone outside, girl. Come on.

1:05:53.704 --> 1:05:57.124
They brought out that big cage.
'Tis up on a stage.

1:05:58.125 --> 1:05:59.543
Oh, no.

1:06:08.969 --> 1:06:12.222
Listen to me! I'm the best soldier!

1:06:12.306 --> 1:06:16.310
Push! Push! A little further.

1:06:17.978 --> 1:06:20.647
Good. That's enough. Step away.

1:06:20.731 --> 1:06:22.357
Return to your positions.

1:06:23.650 --> 1:06:27.112
-Mebh, stop! Please.
-My mammy's here! Get off of me!

1:06:27.196 --> 1:06:28.780
Mebh. No!

1:06:30.449 --> 1:06:35.412
People of Kilkenny,
I have heard your concerns.

1:06:35.495 --> 1:06:41.460
Wolf attacks, livestock lost,
a wolf running through our very streets.

1:06:41.543 --> 1:06:44.505
-But listen to me. Have no fear.
-Mebh, stop.

1:06:45.756 --> 1:06:47.007
Get off of me!

1:06:47.090 --> 1:06:48.800
You must get out of here now.

1:06:48.884 --> 1:06:51.970
Let me go. Let me go.

1:06:52.054 --> 1:06:55.724
Hey! Hey! Over here! I've caught a wolf.

1:06:55.807 --> 1:06:59.478
-...a civilized country.
-Look! She caught the wolf.

1:06:59.561 --> 1:07:00.812
We cannot be...

1:07:00.896 --> 1:07:04.024
My fellow hunters,
we have a new wolf to kill.

1:07:04.983 --> 1:07:07.110
No. No! Get off of me!

1:07:09.613 --> 1:07:13.075
I have to find my mammy. Get away from me.

1:07:13.158 --> 1:07:16.328
Robyn, stop. What are you doing?

1:07:17.704 --> 1:07:20.832
I'm gonna eat you all! Let me out!

1:07:20.916 --> 1:07:23.418
Mebh, your mother told me
to keep you safe.

1:07:23.502 --> 1:07:26.046
You liar! You knew!

1:07:27.714 --> 1:07:30.300
This is for your own good. I'm sorry.

1:07:30.384 --> 1:07:32.052
Get the wolf, wolf...

1:07:32.135 --> 1:07:36.181
I have been sent here by the Lord himself

1:07:36.265 --> 1:07:38.934
to conquer the wild.

1:07:39.017 --> 1:07:44.064
And I will show you it can be tamed.
Behold.

1:07:51.071 --> 1:07:52.155
-Wolf!
-Mammy!

1:07:54.032 --> 1:07:55.784
-Kill the wolf!
-Kill the wolf!

1:07:57.536 --> 1:07:58.871
Kill the wolf!

1:07:58.954 --> 1:08:00.080
Kill the beast!

1:08:04.293 --> 1:08:06.170
He has got a wolf.

1:08:06.253 --> 1:08:10.591
Enough! That's enough! Calm! Calm!

1:08:11.550 --> 1:08:14.678
You have nothing to fear from this beast.

1:08:14.761 --> 1:08:17.346
Now, open the gate.

1:08:36.450 --> 1:08:39.036
-Kill that wolf.
-Come on now.

1:08:41.496 --> 1:08:46.667
You see? This once wild creature
is now tamed.

1:08:46.752 --> 1:08:50.339
Obedient. A mere faithful servant.

1:08:52.508 --> 1:08:56.886
I will rid our land
of all its wretched kind.

1:08:56.970 --> 1:08:59.765
Mammy. Mammy! Mammy!

1:09:02.559 --> 1:09:04.060
Mebh, no!

1:09:10.484 --> 1:09:13.319
-Hey!
-Mammy, Mammy. It's me. I'm here.

1:09:13.403 --> 1:09:15.197
-What's this? What's going on here?
-I'm here, Mammy.

1:09:15.279 --> 1:09:18.200
Let her go! That's my mammy!

1:09:19.785 --> 1:09:21.036
Let her go!

1:09:21.662 --> 1:09:24.288
Goodfellowe, take charge
of this wild thing.

1:09:35.341 --> 1:09:38.136
Goodfellowe, can you not catch anything?
What are you doing?

1:09:41.723 --> 1:09:43.642
Collar that demon
and put her in the stock.

1:09:43.725 --> 1:09:46.019
Father! No!

1:09:52.859 --> 1:09:53.861
-Guards!
-Stop!

1:09:53.944 --> 1:09:54.945
Don't move.

1:09:55.571 --> 1:09:57.030
Hold it right there, you wildling.

1:10:00.325 --> 1:10:02.494
Father! Don't! No!

1:10:02.578 --> 1:10:03.829
Robyn! Stay back!

1:10:05.539 --> 1:10:07.916
Father, stop! This is wrong!

1:10:08.000 --> 1:10:09.501
Robyn! Get away from here!

1:10:10.169 --> 1:10:11.461
Whoa!

1:10:15.549 --> 1:10:17.009
-A soldier's been bitten!
-Father!

1:10:17.092 --> 1:10:18.051
The wolf bit him!

1:10:19.928 --> 1:10:21.930
Pull it back. Pull it back.

1:10:22.014 --> 1:10:23.390
-Whoa!
-That's it.

1:10:23.473 --> 1:10:25.142
-Whoa!
-Lock it up!

1:10:25.225 --> 1:10:27.811
-Oh, no, you don't!
-Cover it, now!

1:10:28.645 --> 1:10:29.646
Mammy!

1:10:32.232 --> 1:10:35.277
Mammy. What have they done?

1:10:54.213 --> 1:10:55.464
Come here, you!

1:11:00.177 --> 1:11:02.513
I am a Wolfwalker!

1:11:03.805 --> 1:11:07.559
I'm getting my wolves
and coming back for my mammy!

1:11:07.643 --> 1:11:10.145
Then we'll eat you all!

1:11:22.449 --> 1:11:26.119
People! Listen to me. Listen to me.

1:11:26.203 --> 1:11:30.832
Do not fear wild girls and wolves

1:11:30.916 --> 1:11:34.169
because tonight we put an end to this.

1:11:34.253 --> 1:11:38.090
I will burn this forest to the ground.

1:11:38.173 --> 1:11:41.510
I will lead cannons
to the den of these beasts

1:11:41.593 --> 1:11:44.930
-and send them all to hell.
-No!

1:11:45.013 --> 1:11:48.851
We shall prevail. It is the Lord's will.

1:11:49.393 --> 1:11:51.144
-Prepare a squadron.
-Yes, sir.

1:11:51.228 --> 1:11:52.813
-Move along.
-Get a move on.

1:11:52.896 --> 1:11:54.356
Move along.

1:11:54.439 --> 1:11:58.402
Goodfellowe, what have you become?
You can't even catch a little girl?

1:11:58.944 --> 1:12:01.530
Prove yourself a worthy soldier tonight

1:12:01.613 --> 1:12:03.699
or tomorrow you are in chains.

1:12:03.782 --> 1:12:06.577
Now, put an end to that wild beast.

1:12:06.660 --> 1:12:09.246
What cannot be tamed must be destroyed.

1:12:09.329 --> 1:12:11.623
No, please. You can't.

1:12:11.707 --> 1:12:13.041
Robyn! Stop this.

1:12:13.125 --> 1:12:18.797
And for heaven's sake, put manners on
that girl, or manners will be put on her.

1:12:34.396 --> 1:12:38.734
-Over here. Come on.
-Steady, steady. Move along.

1:12:38.817 --> 1:12:41.820
-Come on, lads. Let's go...
-Off home, you lot.

1:12:41.904 --> 1:12:43.780
Off the castle grounds.

1:12:44.364 --> 1:12:46.283
No, please. Father, please don't.

1:12:46.366 --> 1:12:48.410
Enough. Robyn, return to your duties.

1:12:48.493 --> 1:12:50.579
-But you can't.
-Now, girl!

1:13:08.388 --> 1:13:12.309
Hurry! With that weapon,
our victory is at hand.

1:13:25.697 --> 1:13:27.407
Robyn, what are you doing, girl?

1:13:27.491 --> 1:13:29.993
The Lord Protector will have us in chains.

1:13:30.077 --> 1:13:33.622
He's wrong, Father. All this is wrong.
Don't you see that?

1:13:33.705 --> 1:13:36.416
Robyn, step aside.
We must do what we're told.

1:13:36.500 --> 1:13:38.168
Why, Father? Why?

1:13:38.252 --> 1:13:39.378
I'm afraid.

1:13:40.963 --> 1:13:42.172
I'm afraid.

1:13:42.256 --> 1:13:43.257
Father?

1:13:44.758 --> 1:13:47.135
I won't be here to protect you forever.

1:13:47.219 --> 1:13:50.681
I'm so afraid that one day
you will end up in a cage.

1:13:52.558 --> 1:13:54.393
But I already am in a cage.

1:13:55.519 --> 1:13:57.145
Wolves! Wolves!

1:14:00.065 --> 1:14:01.775
Wolves! Wolves!

1:14:10.284 --> 1:14:11.618
What is happening?

1:14:17.249 --> 1:14:18.750
I'm sorry, Father.

1:14:21.295 --> 1:14:22.546
Robyn!

1:14:22.629 --> 1:14:24.381
-The beast is loose!
-What the...

1:14:25.090 --> 1:14:26.049
No!

1:14:28.343 --> 1:14:29.344
Grab her!

1:14:30.512 --> 1:14:31.805
Cover the gate!

1:14:33.515 --> 1:14:35.851
-Lower the gate!
-Incoming!

1:14:35.934 --> 1:14:36.977
Fire!

1:14:37.060 --> 1:14:38.478
-No!
-Don't let it get away!

1:14:41.148 --> 1:14:43.275
I tried to stop her, but I failed.

1:14:43.358 --> 1:14:44.943
She's gonna get herself killed.

1:14:47.070 --> 1:14:48.655
It's coming this way!

1:14:51.783 --> 1:14:53.619
Go on, then!

1:14:55.162 --> 1:14:56.788
Shut the gates!

1:14:57.581 --> 1:14:59.124
Draw the bridge up!

1:15:03.337 --> 1:15:04.671
Ready your arms!

1:15:04.755 --> 1:15:06.048
Go.

1:15:06.131 --> 1:15:07.341
Fire!

1:15:07.424 --> 1:15:08.967
Aim for the beast!

1:15:12.930 --> 1:15:14.848
-Wolf!
-Watch out!

1:15:33.492 --> 1:15:36.411
It's time for us to attack those townies!

1:15:36.495 --> 1:15:38.038
Let's eat them all!

1:15:38.121 --> 1:15:39.706
They have my--

1:15:44.419 --> 1:15:45.420
Mammy?

1:15:51.301 --> 1:15:52.427
Mammy.

1:15:57.683 --> 1:16:00.936
Mammy! Mammy.

1:16:06.942 --> 1:16:08.193
Mammy, you're back.

1:16:08.277 --> 1:16:09.278
Mebh.

1:16:13.949 --> 1:16:18.495
I thought I would never see you again...
until this one freed me.

1:16:25.127 --> 1:16:27.754
Mebh, I'm so sorry.

1:16:27.838 --> 1:16:32.676
I was only trying to keep you safe.
Trying to help. I didn't know what to do.

1:16:32.759 --> 1:16:33.760
I was...

1:16:35.179 --> 1:16:36.471
I'm sorry, Mebh.

1:16:43.770 --> 1:16:45.647
Come here to me, townie.

1:16:52.487 --> 1:16:54.656
I'm not a townie anymore, Mebh.

1:16:54.740 --> 1:16:56.116
Thanks for helping Mammy.

1:17:02.289 --> 1:17:03.290
No!

1:17:03.373 --> 1:17:07.961
Mammy! No, no!
Mammy, what happened to you? No!

1:17:08.045 --> 1:17:11.089
Mammy! Mammy! No!

1:17:11.173 --> 1:17:12.424
Robyn!

1:17:12.508 --> 1:17:14.218
-Mammy!
-Robyn! Run! Quick!

1:17:14.301 --> 1:17:15.928
Mammy, what happened to you?

1:17:16.011 --> 1:17:17.012
No, Father!

1:17:17.095 --> 1:17:19.097
-Come on, Robyn!
-No, Father!

1:17:19.181 --> 1:17:21.642
-You shot her! How could you?
-Come on! Robyn! Run!

1:17:21.725 --> 1:17:23.227
Let me go! Mebh!

1:17:23.310 --> 1:17:26.021
-I have to help her! Let me go!
-Back!

1:17:26.104 --> 1:17:27.689
-I said back! Stay back!
-No!

1:17:27.773 --> 1:17:29.483
-What have you done?
-Get back!

1:17:29.566 --> 1:17:30.776
Get away from here!

1:18:27.749 --> 1:18:30.043
Stop! No! Let me go!

1:18:30.127 --> 1:18:31.712
-Robyn! No! Stay!
-Stop!

1:18:31.795 --> 1:18:33.380
Mebh!

1:18:33.463 --> 1:18:34.965
No!

1:18:35.048 --> 1:18:37.384
I have to help her! She's dying!

1:18:37.467 --> 1:18:38.468
Come on, Robyn!

1:18:39.219 --> 1:18:40.512
Let me go!

1:18:40.929 --> 1:18:42.681
Mebh! Mebh!

1:18:42.764 --> 1:18:45.225
No, Robyn! Why? I don't understand!

1:18:45.309 --> 1:18:50.022
Don't you see?
I'm one of them. I'm a Wolfwalker.

1:18:50.939 --> 1:18:56.069
No, Robyn. Please.
Stay with me. I can't let you go.

1:18:56.570 --> 1:18:57.571
Father.

1:19:09.917 --> 1:19:10.918
