1:19:14.963 --> 1:19:16.089
Robyn!

1:19:27.559 --> 1:19:29.311
-Forward!
-Ready arms.

1:19:29.895 --> 1:19:31.021
Formation!

1:19:31.688 --> 1:19:35.734
Goodfellowe, have you lost your senses?
What is going on here?

1:19:35.817 --> 1:19:38.070
Robyn, she's gone.

1:19:38.862 --> 1:19:41.740
-Chain him. We'll deal with him later.
-Yes, sir.

1:19:44.076 --> 1:19:45.953
That's a fresh track.

1:19:46.411 --> 1:19:48.789
Move on! Burn it all!

1:19:48.872 --> 1:19:50.374
Yes, sir. Forward.

1:19:50.457 --> 1:19:51.917
-Hold still.
-Forward.

1:19:52.000 --> 1:19:54.795
-Burn the woods!
-Burn it down!

1:20:41.466 --> 1:20:43.719
Oh, God, what have I done?

1:20:43.802 --> 1:20:48.223
Robyn... Robyn, wake up, please. Please.

1:21:02.404 --> 1:21:03.405
Mammy!

1:21:05.532 --> 1:21:07.659
Please, Mammy, breathe.

1:21:09.411 --> 1:21:15.125
I've never healed anything this
bad before. It's gonna take time.

1:21:16.043 --> 1:21:17.628
I'm not leaving you, Mammy.

1:21:35.020 --> 1:21:36.063
I'll hold them off.

1:21:38.232 --> 1:21:39.233
Follow her.

1:21:44.655 --> 1:21:46.198
-Watch it, boys!
-Ready arms!

1:21:46.281 --> 1:21:47.908
Get ready to march!

1:21:53.497 --> 1:21:55.415
They're in there! Advance!

1:21:55.499 --> 1:21:57.584
Aye, sir! Forward, men!

1:22:00.045 --> 1:22:03.590
Continue onward. Push, men! Push!

1:22:07.427 --> 1:22:09.680
We can drive them back. We are wolves!

1:22:09.763 --> 1:22:12.599
-Formation!
-They have guns. A cannon.

1:22:13.851 --> 1:22:17.437
But don't be afraid.
They're in our forest. Let's go!

1:22:20.023 --> 1:22:21.608
-Brave on!
-Push, men, push!

1:22:21.692 --> 1:22:22.734
Keep going!

1:22:23.694 --> 1:22:25.529
Load your weapons.

1:22:26.280 --> 1:22:29.074
-Burn them out. Pick them off!
-Yes, sir!

1:22:29.449 --> 1:22:30.784
-Spread out!
-More fire!

1:22:30.868 --> 1:22:32.828
-Over here!
-Burn it!

1:22:33.662 --> 1:22:35.414
-Burn the woods!
-Onward!

1:22:39.668 --> 1:22:42.588
-Hey, more fire over here!
-Burn it down!

1:22:46.133 --> 1:22:47.759
What on Earth is this?

1:23:01.648 --> 1:23:02.649
Spread out!

1:23:02.733 --> 1:23:04.568
Get more fire going over here!

1:23:05.235 --> 1:23:06.820
Take cover in the trees.

1:23:08.155 --> 1:23:09.698
Use the traps.

1:23:10.407 --> 1:23:11.408
Oh, bloody hell!

1:23:11.491 --> 1:23:12.618
Draw their fire.

1:23:14.119 --> 1:23:16.496
Then strike from the shadows
when they're reloading.

1:23:17.998 --> 1:23:20.584
Report? Report?

1:23:32.846 --> 1:23:33.847
No!

1:23:35.098 --> 1:23:37.351
I can't, Mammy. I can't.

1:23:37.434 --> 1:23:39.019
I'm not strong enough.

1:23:39.102 --> 1:23:42.356
Please, tell me what to do.

1:23:51.740 --> 1:23:53.867
The pack. I need the pack.

1:23:58.038 --> 1:23:59.289
What? What is that?

1:24:03.752 --> 1:24:04.753
Run!

1:24:23.355 --> 1:24:24.940
Dear God. What was that?

1:24:26.733 --> 1:24:28.277
It's a Wolfwalker.

1:24:31.446 --> 1:24:32.865
Witchcraft.

1:24:32.948 --> 1:24:36.493
-Run! Get out of here!
-What do you think you're doing?

1:24:36.577 --> 1:24:38.036
Reform your ranks!

1:24:38.120 --> 1:24:39.621
Get back to your positions!

1:24:39.705 --> 1:24:41.290
-We're surrounded.
-Run!

1:24:47.921 --> 1:24:49.548
Have mercy! Have mercy!

1:24:53.051 --> 1:24:56.388
Fire! Fire at will!

1:24:56.471 --> 1:24:57.723
Fire!

1:24:59.391 --> 1:25:00.601
