1:25:14.114 --> 1:25:15.115
Robyn.

1:25:20.829 --> 1:25:21.997
Robyn, go!

1:25:27.169 --> 1:25:29.838
Gunners, don't let them get away!

1:25:30.547 --> 1:25:33.175
Slay the foul beasts!

1:25:43.227 --> 1:25:47.439
Quick! Everyone, down here.
I need your help.

1:25:53.612 --> 1:25:54.613
Robyn?

1:25:55.280 --> 1:25:56.365
Where's Robyn?

1:26:05.457 --> 1:26:09.002
Men, run and you will be killed!

1:26:09.086 --> 1:26:12.172
Follow my command and we will prevail.

1:26:13.507 --> 1:26:15.425
The Lord is guiding us.

1:26:18.470 --> 1:26:19.638
Robyn.

1:26:20.597 --> 1:26:22.057
Forward!

1:26:22.140 --> 1:26:24.059
-Load the cannon!
-Aye, sir.

1:26:47.791 --> 1:26:51.712
Show yourselves, you wicked creatures.

1:26:51.795 --> 1:26:54.214
Come, meet your end.

1:27:02.306 --> 1:27:05.434
There it is, the devil's lair!

1:27:05.517 --> 1:27:07.728
Our victory is at hand!

1:27:07.811 --> 1:27:09.479
Gunners, fire!

1:27:12.024 --> 1:27:13.483
Take cover!

1:27:15.527 --> 1:27:16.403
Robyn!

1:27:18.405 --> 1:27:19.990
