1:27:29.374 --> 1:27:30.209
No, Robyn!

1:27:40.010 --> 1:27:41.011
Robyn?

1:27:41.094 --> 1:27:42.471
Robyn?

1:27:46.141 --> 1:27:47.726
Robyn, get up.

1:27:57.319 --> 1:27:58.403
