1:28:08.205 --> 1:28:09.456
Foul bird!

1:28:12.876 --> 1:28:14.962
Stop! She's just a girl.

1:28:15.045 --> 1:28:19.842
By God's glory and punishment,
he vanquishes thee.

1:28:20.425 --> 1:28:22.886
Robyn! No!

1:28:39.236 --> 1:28:41.613
Lord God Almighty, protect me.

1:29:41.131 --> 1:29:42.132
