1:31:11.096 --> 1:31:12.222
Father.

1:31:17.853 --> 1:31:19.354
We have to help Mebh.

1:31:38.415 --> 1:31:41.210
Please, Mammy, don't go. Don't go.

1:31:41.752 --> 1:31:43.420
